  <brief_title>Intubation With Storz Videolaryngoscope® Versus Airtraq® - in an Infant Population</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intubation With Storz Videolaryngoscope® Versus Airtraq® - in an Infant Population</official_title>
  <sponsors>
